  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You find yourself existing between the gravitic and photonic extremes of stellar forces, believing that a balance between the two is where one finds perfection. This means that you often swap between attunements in your daily life and enjoy using graviton and photon abilities in an interweaved tapestry.</p><p><strong>Favored Attunement:</strong> Graviton and Photon. Choose which attunement you have outside of combat, and when using the Attune action you can select which attunement you wish to be.</p><p><strong>Revelations</strong>: initial: @UUID[Compendium.starfinder-field-test-for-pf2e.actions.Item.cQMj2w63yyN1A9W3]{Binaric Assault}; advanced: @UUID[Compendium.starfinder-field-test-for-pf2e.actions.Item.QWJQQDh6OcKAiG1r]{Ascended Stability}; greater: @UUID[Compendium.starfinder-field-test-for-pf2e.actions.Item.EvcD5wCRJPM9hAHK]{Astrological Sense}</p><p><strong>Arrangement Skill</strong>: Medicine or Society</p>"
